    DefaultInstantiator<T>
    Instantiator for any class that provide a public accessible default constructor
    ExceptionHelper
    Helper class used for accessing an exception message in a general way
    FactoryBasedInstantiator<T>
    This ParameterizedInstantiator uses a factory method derived by the given RuntimeProperties.getAllProperties() in order to instantiate Objects
    InjectedBeanInstantiator<T>
    Variant of ParameterizedInstantiator that deals with test, where the actual beans to be tested are Injected by cdi, see TestObjectProvider as well
